
Field Types:
- Boolean 
    Default Value
    Unique Value [none, 'true', 'false']
    Description : if set to 'true', one row will be 'true' at the same time
    e.g. : set this row default:true, all the others row will be default:false

- Calculated
    Available operator : +-/*

- Code


Layout
 - Layouts list
 - Default Layout
 - Every page can have a default layout,custom layout or no layout


Lists 
 - ability to edit Field
 - ability to add views, and select which one is the default for each mode (index,view,edit,create,delete)
   the renderer will render the view stored in the database if found and published, otherwise it will render the default one
 - ability to hide a field from a view
          

        